OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham is selecting his Cabinet
OL,7,Fafter replacing Sir Keir Starmer as
OL,8,FPrime Minister.
OL,10,FHere, the Press Association looks at
OL,11,Fthe appointments so far:
OL,13,F` John Healey ` Chancellor
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FA stalwart of Labour's frontbench, Mr
OL,7,FHealey served in the Blair-Brown
OL,8,Fgovernments, as well in as the shadow
OL,9,Fcabinets of Ed Miliband and Jeremy
OL,10,FCorbyn. He then became Sir Keir's
OL,11,Fshadow defence secretary, and then
OL,12,Fdefence secretary after the 2024
OL,13,Fgeneral election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FMr Healey now finds himself leading
OL,7,Fthe Treasury, a department which
OL,8,Fprovoked his exit from Government in
OL,9,FJune. His shock resignation as defence
OL,10,Fsecretary came after a row about
OL,11,Fincreasing defence spending. That
OL,12,Fproved a consequential moment in Sir
OL,13,FKeir's downfall as premier.
OL,15,FA source in Mr Burnham's new ministry
OL,16,Fsaid Mr Healey had been appointed
OL,17,Fbecause he is a trusted and
OL,18,Fexperienced figure within Labour, who
OL,19,Fshares the same outlook as the new
OL,20,FPrime Minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,F` Ed Miliband ` Foreign Secretary
OL,8,FDubbed "Red Ed" by the tabloids during
OL,9,Fhis time as Labour leader, and subject
OL,10,Fto embarrassing photos of him eating a
OL,11,Fbacon sandwich being published in the
OL,12,Fpress in the run up to the 2015
OL,13,Fgeneral election, Mr Miliband returned
OL,14,Fto frontline politics following the
OL,15,FCorbyn era and had served as energy
OL,16,Fsecretary in Sir Keir's government
OL,17,Fsince Labour's election win in 2024,
OL,18,Fspearheading the net zero agenda.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FHe now moves to the role of Foreign
OL,7,FSecretary, effectively Britain's top
OL,8,Fdiplomat. Mr Miliband is said to have
OL,9,Fbeen appointed the new Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary because of his experience of
OL,11,Finternational leadership and
OL,12,Fnegotiating with other nations across
OL,13,Fthe world during his time as energy
OL,14,Fsecretary.
OL,16,F` Shabana Mahmood ` Home Secretary
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FMs Mahmood remains as Home Secretary
OL,7,Funder Mr Burnham. In that role, she
OL,8,Fhas led the Government's work on
OL,9,Fcreating stricter migration controls.
OL,10,FAs Labour's efforts to tackle smuggler
OL,11,Fgangs have borne fruit in reducing
OL,12,FChannel crossings, calls from
OL,13,Fbackbench Labour MPs to soften new
OL,14,Fmigration curbs could prove an early
OL,15,Fflashpoint for Ms Mahmood and the new
OL,16,FPrime Minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FOxford-educated former barrister Ms
OL,7,FMahmood served as justice secretary
OL,8,Fwhen Labour first won power, before
OL,9,Fher appointment as Home Secretary. She
OL,10,Fis one of the first Muslim women
OL,11,Felected to the Commons, having won the
OL,12,Fseat of Birmingham Ladywood in 2010.
OL,14,F` Louise Haigh ` Chancellor of the
OL,15,FDuchy of Lancaster, and First
OL,16,FSecretary of State
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FMs Haigh became a key figure in Mr
OL,7,FBurnham's plans to return to
OL,8,FWestminster and enter Downing Street,
OL,9,Fand was dubbed part of a group of
OL,10,F"northern power women" who had
OL,11,Fmasterminded the campaign by the new
OL,12,FPrime Minister when he won the
OL,13,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/34
