FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FShe has criticised what she described
OL,7,Fas a boys' club culture at the heart
OL,8,Fof Sir Keir's No 10 operation, after
OL,9,Fshe was forced to resign as transport
OL,10,Fsecretary over a historic criminal
OL,11,Foffence related to incorrectly telling
OL,12,Fpolice that a work mobile phone was
OL,13,Fstolen in 2013.
OL,15,FMs Haigh is expected to drive Mr
OL,16,FBurnham's priorities for Government
OL,17,Facross the Whitehall machine,
OL,18,Fincluding the devolution agenda and
OL,19,Fplans to tackle the cost-of-living
OL,20,Fcrisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,F` Yvette Cooper ` Health Secretary
OL,8,FMs Cooper, who served as home
OL,9,Fsecretary then foreign secretary in
OL,10,FSir Keir's government, has been moved
OL,11,Fto the Cabinet post overseeing health
OL,12,Fand social care in what is considered
OL,13,Fby some Westminster watchers as a
OL,14,Fdemotion from one of the four "great
OL,15,Foffices of state".
OL,17,FShe was viewed as a rising star under
OL,18,FNew Labour, and she served in the
OL,19,FBlair and Brown governments alongside
OL,20,FMr Burnham, before being relegated to
OL,21,Fthe backbenches under Jeremy Corbyn.
OL,26,@vD@_OUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FMs Cooper has been trusted with
OL,7,Foverhauling the social care sector, an
OL,8,Farea which Mr Burnham has said will be
OL,9,Fone of his priorities as Prime
OL,10,FMinister.
OL,12,F` Pat McFadden ` Work and Pensions
OL,13,FSecretary
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/34
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
