PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FLisa Nandy, who has kept her job as
OL,7,FCulture Secretary and is a close ally
OL,8,Fof the Prime Minister, was seen as
OL,9,Fsomething of an outsider in Sir Keir's
OL,10,Fcabinet, and her Greater Manchester
OL,11,Fconstituency of Wigan borders Mr
OL,12,FBurnham's in Makerfield.
OL,14,FAfter Labour's defeat in the 2019
OL,15,Fgeneral election, Ms Nandy stood in
OL,16,Fthe leadership election to replace
OL,17,FJeremy Corbyn, but she finished third
OL,18,Fbehind Sir Keir.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/34
