OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FWhile in opposition, Sir Keir demoted
OL,7,FMs Nandy from shadow foreign secretary
OL,8,Fto shadow levelling up secretary and
OL,9,Fthen shadow cabinet minister for
OL,10,Finternational development.
OL,12,FWes Streeting- Defence Secretary
OL,14,FWes Streeting, who has been appointed
OL,15,Fas Defence Secretary, was initially
OL,16,Fseen as Mr Burnham's main potential
OL,17,Frival but ruled himself out of the
OL,18,FLabour leadership contest shortly
OL,19,Fafter Sir Keir announced his
OL,20,Fresignation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/34
