OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784607479
OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FHe had previously repeatedly insisted
OL,7,Fhe had the 81 names required to mount
OL,8,Fa leadership bid, and spent weeks
OL,9,Fafter resigning from Government
OL,10,Fsetting out his stall.
OL,12,FMr Streeting quit as Heath Secretary
OL,13,Fin May telling Sir Keir in his
OL,14,Fresignation letter that "it is now
OL,15,Fclear that you will not lead the
OL,16,FLabour Party into the next general
OL,17,Felection" and days later told
OL,18,Freporters that he would enter a
OL,19,Fcontest to replace Sir Keir.
OL,21,FAlex Norris ` Justice Secretary
