OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FAlex Norris, who has been appointed as
OL,7,FJustice Secretary, previously served
OL,8,Fas Minister of State for Border
OL,9,FSecurity and Asylum.
OL,11,FEarlier this month, Mr Norris said
OL,12,F"all options are on the table"
OL,13,Fregarding the deportation of Rochdale
OL,14,Fgrooming gang leader Shabir Ahmed who
OL,15,Fwas released from prison.
