OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FDame Angela served as Minister of
OL,7,FState for Pensions and Ageing Society
OL,8,Ffrom June 2009 until May 2010 under
OL,9,FGordon Brown.
OL,11,FShe announced a leadership challenge
OL,12,Fto Jeremy Corbyn in July 2016, but
OL,13,Fwithdrew eight days later leaving Owen
OL,14,FSmith to challenge Mr Corbyn for the
OL,15,Fleadership.
OL,17,FDame Angela has been the MP for
OL,18,FWallasey in Merseyside since 1992.
