OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FMiatta Fahnbulleh, who resigned as a
OL,7,Fhousing minister in protest at Sir
OL,8,FKeir's leadership earlier this year,
OL,9,Fhas been advising Mr Burnham and
OL,10,Ffleshing out his policy plans.
OL,12,FMs Fahnbulleh, the new Energy
OL,13,FSecretary, is considered to be a
OL,14,Fmember of Mr Burnham's inner circle.
OL,16,FShe previously served as a
OL,17,Fparliamentary under-secretary of state
OL,18,Fin the Ministry of Housing,
OL,19,FCommunities and Local Government and
OL,20,Fis also considered to be a close ally
OL,21,Fof Ed Miliband.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/34
