OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,F` Ellie Reeves ` Attorney General
OL,8,FEllie Reeves, sister of former
OL,9,Fchancellor Rachel Reeves, has served
OL,10,Fas Solicitor General since September
OL,11,F2025.
OL,13,FA former barrister, she previously
OL,14,Fserved as Chair of the Labour Party
OL,15,Fand, while Labour was in opposition,
OL,16,Fas shadow solicitor general and shadow
OL,17,Fminister for prisons and probation.
