OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FSwindon South MP Heidi Alexander will
OL,7,Fremain Transport Secretary, a post she
OL,8,Fhas held since November 2024.
OL,10,FShe previously served alongside Andy
OL,11,FBurnham in Ed Miliband's shadow
OL,12,FCabinet before being appointed shadow
OL,13,Fhealth ecretary by Jeremy Corbyn in
OL,14,F2015.
OL,16,FAfter returning to Parliament at the
OL,17,F2024 general election, Ms Alexander
OL,18,Fbriefly served as Justice Secretary
OL,19,Fbefore moving to the transport brief.
