OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FSir Chris Bryant ` Northern Ireland
OL,7,FSecretary
OL,9,FThe former Anglican priest has been
OL,10,Fthe MP for Rhondda and Ogmore, and
OL,11,Fpreviously Rhondda, in Wales, since
OL,12,F2001.
OL,14,FEarlier this month, he said the
OL,15,FGovernment was "actively considering"
OL,16,Fa ban on trade with illegal Israeli
OL,17,Fsettlements, but suggested there were
OL,18,Fchallenges around determining the
OL,19,Fsource of goods.
