OL,6,FSir Chris was previously Minister of
OL,7,FState for Trade and earlier this year
OL,8,Fdescribed Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor
OL,9,Fas "a rude, arrogant and entitled man
OL,10,Fwho could not distinguish between the
OL,11,Fpublic interest, which he said he
