OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FDouglas Alexander, who has been
OL,7,Freappointed as Secretary of State for
OL,8,FScotland, previously served as
OL,9,FChancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster,
OL,10,FTransport Secretary and International
OL,11,FDevelopment Secretary in the cabinets
OL,12,Fof Tony Blair and Gordon Brown.
OL,14,FScotland's First Minister John Swinney
OL,15,Fsaid on Monday that relations with
OL,16,FWestminster had deteriorated over the
OL,17,Flast year as he signalled he did not
OL,18,Fwant Mr Alexander to return as
OL,19,FScottish secretary in Mr Burnham's
OL,20,FGovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G32/34
