OL,3,CWho has Andy Burnham picked to be in
OL,4,Chis Cabinet?
OL,6,FLast month, Mr Alexander admitted to
OL,7,Fan "oversight" in failing to declare
OL,8,Ffor a year-and-a-half that he had met
OL,9,FLord Peter Mandelson's lobbying firm.
OL,11,F` Stephen Kinnock ` Wales Secretary
OL,13,FStephen Kinnock will replace Jo
OL,14,FStevens as Welsh Secretary after two
OL,15,Fyears in the role.
OL,17,FMr Kinnock is the son of former Labour
OL,18,Fleader Neil Kinnock and is married to
OL,19,FHelle Thorning-Schmidt, a former
OL,20,FDanish prime minister.
